These are Puzzles for 2x7 Level 4

.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-4-1::.
The people use 7 different means of transport: bus, bike, quad-bike, car, tram, airplane, helicopter
The people have 7 different jobs:  engineer, police-officer, chef, dressmaker, teacher, nurse, mechanic
 1. the chef is on the left of the person driving the helicopter##1
 2. the chef is on the right of the teacher##1
 3. the chef is on the left or right of the person driving the quad-bike##3
 4. the mechanic is the person driving the bus##1
 5. the police-officer is the person driving the car##1
 6. the engineer is in the middle##1
 7. the dressmaker is on the far left or far right##3
 8. the person driving the quad-bike is in an even position##4
 9. the nurse is in an odd position##4
10. the nurse is on the left or right of the mechanic##3
11. the person driving the bus is on the right of the nurse##1
12. the person driving the quad-bike is the teacher##1
13. the person driving the helicopter is on the right of the person driving the airplane##1
14. the person driving the tram is on the left or right of the person driving the quad-bike##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |     2      |    3    |     4     |     5      |    6    |    7    |
| Transport   | tram      | quad-bike      | airplane    | helicopter    | bike | bus     | car     |
| Job   | dressmaker | teacher | chef | engineer | nurse   | mechanic | police-officer |

