.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-4-2::.
The people prefer 7 different types of sport: rugby, water-polo, tennis, surfing, snowboarding, weightlifting, lacrosse
The people grow 7 different varities of flowers: aconite, orchid, begonia, daffodil, rose, balloon-flower, azalea
 1. the person who's sport is tennis is on the left or right of the person who's sport is water-polo##3
 2. the person who growsaconite is on the left or right of the person who's sport is surfing##3
 3. the person who growsrose is in an odd position##4
 4. the person who growsbegonia is on the left or right of the person who growsdaffodil##3
 5. the person who's sport is snowboarding is on the far left or far right##3
 6. the person who growsballoon-flower is the person who's sport is surfing##1
 7. the person who's sport is water-polo is the person who growsrose##1
 8. the person who's sport is weightlifting is on the left of the person who growsdaffodil##1
 9. the person who's sport is surfing is the person who growsballoon-flower##1
10. the person who's sport is tennis is between the person who growsballoon-flower and the person who's sport is water-polo##2
11. the person who's sport is weightlifting is in the middle##1
12. the person who growsazalea is on the far left or far right##3
13. the person who's sport is water-polo is on the far left or far right##3
14. the person who's sport is lacrosse is on the right of the person who growsorchid##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |      2       |    3    |     4      |      5      |     6     |   7    |
| Sport   | water-polo   | tennis | surfing | weightlifting   | lacrosse | rugby | snowboarding |
| Flower           | rose | aconite          | balloon-flower    | orchid | daffodil     | begonia      | azalea    |

