.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-4-3::.
The people grow 7 different varities of flowers: tulip, poppy, daffodil, balloon-flower, azalea, rose, sunflower
The people prefer 7 different music-genres: indie, disco, techno, metal, soul, jazz, punk
 1. the fan of techno is on the right of the fan of punk##1
 2. the fan of punk is on the left or right of the person who growsdaffodil##3
 3. the person who growspoppy is on the left or right of the fan of indie##3
 4. the person who growspoppy is between the person who growsrose and the person who growsballoon-flower##2
 5. the fan of jazz is on the left or right of the fan of disco##3
 6. the fan of techno is on the right of the person who growsrose##1
 7. the fan of soul is in an odd position##4
 8. the fan of indie is on the far left##1
 9. the fan of disco is the person who growstulip##1
10. the person who growstulip is on the far right##1
11. the fan of jazz is the person who growssunflower##1
12. the fan of soul is between the person who growsdaffodil and the person who growssunflower##2

.:: Answer ::.
|        |      1      |     2     |     3     |    4     |       5        |        6        |     7      |
| Flower   | balloon-flower        | poppy  | rose | daffodil | azalea           | sunflower           | tulip  |
| Music-Genre    | indie | metal | punk   | techno    | soul | jazz | disco |

