 1. the dannemann-smoker is on the left or right of the cain-smoker##3
 2. the dannemann-smoker is on the left or right of the swisher-smoker##3
 3. the person drinking almond-milk is on the right of the chaman-smoker##1
 4. the person drinking hot-chocolate is on the far left or far right##3
 5. the swisher-smoker is in an even position##4
 6. the dannemann-smoker is on the left or right of the person drinking lemonade##3
 7. the person drinking almond-milk is in an odd position##4
 8. the person drinking iced-tea is on the far right##1
 9. the swisher-smoker is on the right of the davidoff-smoker##1
10. the person drinking fanta is on the left of the cain-smoker##1
11. the chaman-smoker is on the right of the bongani-smoker##1
12. the bongani-smoker is on the far left##1
13. the oliveros-smoker is on the left or right of the person drinking soy-milk##3

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1    |     2      |      3      |     4      |      5       |      6      |      7      |
| Cigar   | bongani | chaman    | davidoff | swisher | dannemann      | cain | oliveros |
| Beverage     | hot-chocolate  | milk | almond-milk   | lemonade  | fanta | soy-milk     | iced-tea    |

