.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-4-6::.
7 different pets are kept: fish, bird, frog, goldfish, hedgehog, horse, turtle
There are 7 different favourite colors: amber, emerald, black, pink, lilac, fuchsia, white
 1. the person who likes lilac is on the right of the owner of the goldfish##1
 2. the owner of the turtle is the person who likes emerald##1
 3. the person who likes fuchsia is between the person who likes emerald and the owner of the horse##2
 4. the person who likes amber is on the left or right of the person who likes fuchsia##3
 5. the owner of the bird is between the owner of the hedgehog and the owner of the horse##2
 6. the person who likes lilac is in an even position##4
 7. the owner of the goldfish is the person who likes black##1
 8. the owner of the frog is on the left or right of the owner of the turtle##3
 9. the person who likes white is in the middle##1
10. the owner of the hedgehog is on the left of the person who likes white##1
11. the owner of the bird is in an even position##4
12. the person who likes amber is in an odd position##4
13. the person who likes fuchsia is the owner of the frog##1
14. the owner of the goldfish is on the far left##1
15. the owner of the goldfish is on the far left or far right##3
16. the owner of the turtle is on the right of the person who likes fuchsia##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |     2     |    3    |    4     |     5     |  6   |    7     |
| Pet          | goldfish | fish | hedgehog | bird | horse | frog | turtle |
| Color   | black   | lilac      | pink     | white    | amber | fuchsia  | emerald      |

