 2. the person who growssunflower is on the left or right of the person who growspoppy##3
 3. the person who growsorchid is on the left or right of the person who growsazalea##3
 4. the cain-smoker is on the left or right of the davidoff-smoker##3
 5. the old-henry-smoker is on the right of the person who growsazalea##1
 6. the person who growsbellflower is on the left of the bolivar-smoker##1
 7. the siglo-smoker is in an even position##4
 8. the davidoff-smoker is on the left or right of the person who growssunflower##3
 9. the person who growsazalea is on the far left##1
10. the aristoff-smoker is between the person who growsbellflower and the old-henry-smoker##2
11. the davidoff-smoker is on the right of the bolivar-smoker##1
12. the davidoff-smoker is on the left of the person who growsbegonia##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1     |     2     |    3     |   4   |    5    |       6       |      7      |
| Cigar   | bongani     | old-henry   | aristoff      | siglo | bolivar    | davidoff | cain |
| Flower       | azalea | orchid | daisy | bellflower  | sunflower | poppy     | begonia    |

