.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-4-19::.
The people have 7 different hobbies: singing, hiking, board-games, filmmaking, skydiving, reading, sudoku
7 different brands of cigars are smoked: dannemann, game, bluemaster, old-henry, aristoff, fonseca, davidoff
 1. the person who's hobby is hiking is the fonseca-smoker##1
 2. the person who's hobby is skydiving is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is reading##3
 3. the aristoff-smoker is the person who's hobby is sudoku##1
 4. the davidoff-smoker is the person who's hobby is reading##1
 5. the aristoff-smoker is in the middle##1
 6. the bluemaster-smoker is on the far right##1
 7. the person who's hobby is filmmaking is in an odd position##4
 8. the person who's hobby is skydiving is the bluemaster-smoker##1
 9. the aristoff-smoker is on the left of the game-smoker##1
10. the old-henry-smoker is on the left of the person who's hobby is hiking##1
11. the fonseca-smoker is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is filmmaking##3
12. the person who's hobby is filmmaking is in an odd position##4
13. the aristoff-smoker is on the right of the person who's hobby is singing##1
14. the old-henry-smoker is on the far left or far right##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |    2    |     3     |    4    |     5     |    6    |    7    |
| Hobby          | filmmaking  | hiking | singing     | sudoku  | board-games | reading    | skydiving  |
| Cigar   | old-henry | fonseca  | dannemann | aristoff | game | davidoff | bluemaster |

