.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-4-20::.
7 different brands of cigars are smoked: swisher, prince, chaman, davidoff, game, cain, ritmeester
7 different games are played: mah-jongg, poker, chess, billiard, bridge, whist, scrabble
 1. the person playing scrabble is on the left or right of the person playing whist##3
 2. the swisher-smoker is on the left or right of the game-smoker##3
 3. the game-smoker is on the left or right of the person playing chess##3
 4. the person playing bridge is on the far left##1
 5. the davidoff-smoker is the person playing poker##1
 6. the person playing mah-jongg is on the left of the davidoff-smoker##1
 7. the person playing bridge is on the left of the person playing scrabble##1
 8. the prince-smoker is on the right of the game-smoker##1
 9. the cain-smoker is in an odd position##4
10. the ritmeester-smoker is on the right of the person playing scrabble##1
11. the ritmeester-smoker is on the left or right of the person playing chess##3
12. the person playing poker is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |     2     |     3     |    4     |   5    |      6      |    7     |
| Cigar          | cain   | chaman | ritmeester | swisher | game | prince | davidoff |
| Game   | bridge | scrabble      | whist     | chess  | billiard | mah-jongg         | poker    |

 